        <p class="concept-p">A premium companion for pool chemistry. <b>Water reported like weather</b> — quiet, precise, without alarm.</p>
        <p class="concept-p">These are the <b>actual components</b>: they lift out of the running shell and keep working, tethered to their voids.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="rail-head">Details</div>
        <div class="detail-row"><span class="dot"></span><span>Real DOM · FLIP explode · 4 key parts</span></div>
        <div class="detail-row"><span class="dot"></span><span>Live WebGL water shader</span></div>
        <div class="detail-row"><span class="dot"></span><span>Fraunces readings · Instrument Sans actions</span></div>
